                  <li><a class="btn btn-warning btn-sm" value="G">Key of G</a></li>
                  <li><a class="btn btn-warning btn-sm" value="Ab">Key of Ab</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>          
            <br>
          <br>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="chart col-sm-6">
                <h3>1  &nbsp;&nbsp;4 &nbsp;&nbsp;5</h3>
                <h3><span class="number" value="1">C</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="4">F</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="5">G</span></h3>
                <p>Very common in pop music.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="chart col-sm-6">
                <h3>2 &nbsp;&nbsp;5  &nbsp;&nbsp;1</h3>
                <h3><span class="number" value="2">D</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="5">G</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="1">C</span></h3>
                <p>Very common in jazz.</p>
              </div>
            </div><!--/.row-->
            <div class="row">
            <div class="chart col-sm-6">
              <h3>1 &nbsp;&nbsp;5  &nbsp;&nbsp;6- &nbsp;&nbsp;4</h3>
              <h3><span class="number" value="1">C</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="5">G</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="6">A</span><span>m</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="4">F</span></h3>
              <p>Very common in pop music.</p>
            </div>
              <div class="chart col-sm-6">
                <h3>6 &nbsp;&nbsp;2  &nbsp;&nbsp;5 &nbsp;&nbsp;1</h3>
                <h3><span class="number" value="6">A</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="2">D</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="5">G</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="number" value="1">C</span></h3>
                <p>Circle of fourths.</p>
              </div>
            </div><!--/.row-->
